程序包 org.apache.http.conn.routing

Client connection routing APIs.

请参阅: 说明

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    HttpRouteDirector
    Provides directions on establishing a route.
    HttpRoutePlanner
    Encapsulates logic to compute a HttpRoute to a target host.
    RouteInfo
    Read-only interface for route information.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    BasicRouteDirector
    Basic HttpRouteDirector implementation.
    HttpRoute
    The route for a request.
    RouteTracker
    Helps tracking the steps in establishing a route.
  • 枚举概要 
    枚举 说明
    RouteInfo.LayerType
    The layering type of a route.
    RouteInfo.TunnelType
    The tunnelling type of a route.
